name: SPACE ATTACK
description: This is the result of a messed up light photo and a paint mix from my daughter. More than the result, it is a artwork that I loved to make, I felt a real well being. It was also the first time that I accepted to like the result of what I had done. Starting from something that was a failure and making it a success! PNG SIZE : 2275 x 3218 300pp - 13.6Mo
